### Создать клуб (ROLE_ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "HC Test Club",
  "address": "Minsk, Belarus",
  "description": "Test hockey club"
}

### Получить список клубов с пагинацией (ROLE_ADMIN, ROLE_METHODIST)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Получить клуб по ID (ROLE_ADMIN, ROLE_METHODIST)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs/{{clubId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Обновить клуб (ROLE_ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs/{{clubId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "Updated address, Minsk",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Загрузить логотип клуба (ROLE_ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs/{{clubId}}/logo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="logo.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test-logo.png
--boundary--

### Получить логотип клуба (ROLE_ADMIN, ROLE_METHODIST)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs/{{clubId}}/logo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}